Package: hiringLetter
Type: Package
Title: Sorting and Customizing Acceptance or Rejection Letter Templates
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ramya Subramanian
Maintainer: The package maintainer <rsubramanian23@usf.edu>
Description: This package holds a shiny app function for individuals on a hiring committee to
    interactively set qualifications to filter candidates for a position. The default qualifications
    available in the hire function are age, work experience, and current role. The output is filtered
    tables of accepted and rejected individuals with customized acceptance and rejection letter templates.
    The letter template is designed based on a S4 class.
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: dplyr
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3

